235
00:14:24,942 --> 00:14:27,111
You got money problems.

236
00:14:27,111 --> 00:14:31,621
That hair sweeping job isn't gonna help 
you out, but I know about other stuff.

237
00:14:31,621 --> 00:14:33,631
Real stuff that could help you out.

238
00:14:33,631 --> 00:14:35,881
She's not like that.
Take a chill.

239
00:14:35,881 --> 00:14:38,886
Okay, I can see that 
she's classy, okay?

240
00:14:38,886 --> 00:14:41,382
You don't have to point it out.

241
00:14:48,085 --> 00:14:50,267
I wanna go.

242
00:14:51,060 --> 00:14:52,662
Now.

243
00:14:52,662 --> 00:14:54,556
Why?

244
00:14:55,487 --> 00:14:56,988
